"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Dez 21, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mrx1665702743538.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mrx1665702743538.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mrx1665702743538.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mrx1665702743538\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"mrx1665702743538__sessioncookie_481017\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies whether cookies can be accepted by the client browser.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mrx1665702743538__topic_d147539e1_d147540e1_d147541e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mrx1665702743538__p_d147542e1_d147543e1_d147544e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;init-param&gt;\n &lt;param-name&gt;</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">SESSIONCOOKIE</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/param-name&gt;\n &lt;param-value&gt;</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">TRUE</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">FALSE</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">DYNAMIC</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;/param-value&gt;\n &lt;/init-param&gt;</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mrx1665702743538__p_d147545e1_d147546e1_d147547e1\">Default value if omitted: <code class=\"ph codeph\">TRUE</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mrx1665702743538__topic_d106367e1_d106368e1_d106369e1_d106370e1_d106371e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d653805e85\">Values</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mrx1665702743538__li_d51218e1_d51219e1_d51220e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">TRUE</code>—enable Cookie-based state management\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mrx1665702743538__li_d51221e1_d51222e1_d51223e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">FALSE</code>—enable URL-based state management\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"mrx1665702743538__li_d51224e1_d51225e1_d51226e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mrx1665702743538__p_d147551e1_d147552e1_d147553e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">DYNAMIC</code>—enable dynamic state management, where the WRD determines per request to use cookie-based or URL-based state management.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zah1665702685225.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Uniface URL-Based State Management</a><p>A session is a lasting connection between a Web user and Uniface Web Application Server. It starts when a user starts to access a Web application and ends when the browser is closed, the time is expired, or the user logs out. Uniface generates a session ID for each session.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530050\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530050\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "SESSIONCOOKIE Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Dez 21, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies whether cookies can be accepted by the client browser. <init-param> <param-name> SESSIONCOOKIE </param-name> <param-value> TRUE | FALSE | DYNAMIC </param-value> </init-param> Default value if omitted: TRUE Values TRUE —enable Cookie-based state management FALSE —enable URL-based state management DYNAMIC —enable dynamic state management, where the WRD determines per request to use cookie-based or URL-based state management. Related Links Uniface URL-Based State Management A session is a lasting connection between a Web user and Uniface Web Application Server. It starts when a user starts to access a Web application and ends when the browser is closed, the time is expired, or the user logs out. Uniface generates a session ID for each session. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}